      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS GRAHAM (3) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at this track over 400m behind Kiss And Run (23.49) in a Grade 5. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Has ability and is a key runner. CRANKY CRUISER (6) finds it hard to win. Finished in the money last time though when third (23.76) at this track. Form at the trip sound including seven wins. Expected to feature again. LIMEBURNER TOPAZ (1) generally breaks well and with clear running can clear the draw. Latest effort finished 5th in a Grade 5 on May 22 over 272m at this track behind Runaway Sam beaten 6 lengths (16.40). Looks one of the chances. BELLA RORY (8) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
